'Yan majalisa a Wales suna tsoron zama kamar 'yan mata.
Wasu 'yan majalisa sun firgita da shawarar cewa za a canza taken aikinsu daga AMs zuwa MWPs (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan damuwa ta taso ne sakamakon shirye-shiryen canza sunan majalisar dokokin zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisa a duk bangarorin siyasa na fargabar cewa za a yi musu ba'a.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce jama'arsa na tsoron cewa zai yi tasiri a kan jam'iyyun Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: a cikin Welsh, twp yana nufin wawa kuma pwp yana nufin kuraje.
Wani dan majalisa daga jam'iyyar FLAID Kamari ya ce dukkan 'yan majalisarsa ba su gamsu ba kuma sun ba da wasu hanyoyin.
Wani dan majalisa na Welsh Conservative ya ce 'yan majalisa suna shirye su canza sunan, amma sun ce sunan MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament) yana kama da kalmar Muppet (Muppet).
A wannan yanayin, ana furta harafin Welsh w kamar yadda ake furta harafin u a Turanci a cikin lafazi na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin majalisar, wanda ke shirya dokar sauya sunaye, ya ce: "Hukumar karshe game da duk wani bayanin da ya shafi sunayen mukaman 'yan majalisa ita ce, a bayyane yake, shawarar' yan majalisa da kansu".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da ikon canza sunan majalisar dokokin Wales.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya ba da sakamakon shawarwarin jama'a game da shawarwarin, wanda ya ba da goyon baya mai yawa don canza sunan majalisar zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
Game da taken aikin 'yan majalisa (AMs), kwamitin ya ba da shawarar "Welsh MPs" ko kuma WMPs, amma zaɓi na MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi yawa a cikin shawarwari da jama'a.
'Yan majalisa na bayar da shawarwari, amma gwagwarmayar cimma matsaya na iya haifar da ciwon kai ga shugaban kwamitin, Ellen Jones, wanda za ta gabatar da dokar da ta dace a makonni masu zuwa.
Dokar ta kawo wasu canje-canje ga yadda majalisar dokokin ke aiki, ciki har da dokokin dakatar da 'yan majalisa da tsarin kwamitocin.
Zabe na 'yan majalisa ne zai yanke shawarar taken aikinsu a lokacin tattaunawar majalisa.
'Yan Macedonia za su kada kuri'a a zaben raba gardama kan sauya sunan kasar
A ranar Lahadi ne 'yan kasar za su kada kuri'ar ko za su sauya sunan kasarsu zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia.
An yi zaben ne a wani yunƙuri na warware wata takaddama da ta shafe shekaru da dama da makwabciyarta Girka, inda akwai wata ƙasa mai suna Macedonia.
Girka ta dade tana ikirarin cewa yankin da take zaune a arewacin kasar yana da'awar yankin Girka kuma ta sake adawa da yunƙurin Macedonia na shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Shugaban Macedonia, George Ivanov, wanda ya yi adawa da kuri'ar raba gardamar game da sauya sunan, ya ce zai yi watsi da sakamakon.
Duk da haka, masu goyon bayan kuri'ar, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zeib, sun ce sauya sunan kawai farashin da za a biya don shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
