Wani kifi mai suna shark ya ji wa wani yaro mai shekaru 13 rauni a lokacin da yake ruwa don kama lobster
Wani kifi mai suna shark ya kai hari kuma ya ji wa wani yaro dan shekara 13 rauni a ranar Asabar lokacin da yaron ya nutse don kama lobster a California a ranar farko ta kakar wasan lobster, in ji jami'ai.
An kai harin ne da misalin karfe 7 na safiyar yau kusa da bakin tekun Beacon a birnin Ansinitas.
Chad Hamel ya shaida wa gidan talabijin na KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa ya yi ruwa tare da abokansa tun misalin karfe ɗaya na safiyar Asabar, lokacin da ya ji yaron yana kuka don taimako sannan ya shiga can tare da wasu mutane don su taimaka masa ya isa bakin teku.
Hamel ya fara tunanin cewa muryoyin murna ne kawai game da kama wani lobster, amma daga baya ya fahimci cewa yaron yana ihu "An cije ni!"
An cije ni!
Hamel ya ce lokacin da ya kusanci yaron ya ga cewa an cire dukkan kashinsa.
"Na yi ihu ga kowa ya fita daga cikin ruwa: 'Akwai shark a cikin ruwa!'", Hamel ya kara da cewa.
An kai yaron asibitin Radie dake San Diego inda aka bayyana shi a matsayin mutum.
Ba a san irin kifin da ya kai wa yaron hari ba.
Shugaban ceto Larry Giles ya ce a wata sanarwa da ya fitar, an ga wani kifi a yankin makonni da suka gabata, amma an tabbatar da cewa ba kifi ne mai hadari ba.
Giles ya kara da cewa wanda aka kashe ya samu raunuka a jikinsa.
Hukumomi sun rufe hanyar zuwa gabar teku daga Ponto Beach a Kasblad zuwa Swami Beach a Assiniquitas na tsawon awanni 48 don bincike da kuma dalilai na tsaro.
Giles ya lura cewa akwai nau'in kifi fiye da 135 a yankin, amma yawancin ba su da haɗari.
Sainsbury's na shirin shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliya a Burtaniya
Sainsbury's ya fara gasa da Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams kuma ya buɗe hanyoyin shagon kare tare da ƙwararrun mata masu siyarwa.
A wani gagarumin yunkuri na shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya mai kimanin fam biliyan 2.8 a shekara, wanda ke ci gaba da bunkasa yayin da tallace-tallace a cikin kayan kwalliya da kayan gida ke raguwa, za a gwada fadada kayan kwalliyar a shaguna 11 a duk fadin kasar, kuma idan gwajin ya yi nasara, za a kara wasu shaguna a shekara mai zuwa.
Wannan zuba jari a kayayyakin kwalliya ya zo ne a daidai lokacin da masu sayar da kayayyaki ke neman hanyoyin amfani da wuraren da talabijin da microwave da kayayyakin gida suka sha a baya.
Sainsbury's ya ce ana sa ran kamfanin zai ninka kayan kwalliyar sa zuwa kayayyaki 3,000, gami da alamomi kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw a karon farko a tarihin sa.
Layin samfuran L'Oreal , Maybelline da Burt's Bees suma za su sami ƙarin yanki tare da yankuna na musamman kamar waɗanda ke cikin shaguna kamar Boots.
Har ila yau, kamfanin sayar da kayayyaki ya sake sake fasalin kayan kwalliyarsa - Boutique - don yawancin kayayyakin su kasance masu jin daɗin yanayi, wanda ya zama sananne ga matasa masu sayayya.
Bugu da kari, dillalan turare na Fragrance Shop za su duba lasisi a shagunan Sainsbury's guda biyu, wanda na farko ya buɗe a Croydon, Kudancin London, a makon da ya gabata kuma na biyu zai buɗe a Slee Oak, Birmingham, a ƙarshen wannan shekarar.
Kasuwancin kan layi da kuma sayen ƙananan kayan abinci a kowace rana a cikin shagunan da ke kusa da su suna buƙatar masu sayarwa su yi aiki sosai don su sa mutane su ziyarce su.
Mike Cope, Shugaba na Sainsbury's, ya ce rassan za su zama kamar kantin sayar da kaya yayin da babban kanti ke ƙoƙarin yin gwagwarmaya da manyan kantunan Aldi da Lidl tare da ƙarin kayan aiki da kayayyaki ba abinci ba.
Sainsbury's ya kara wuraren sayar da kayayyaki na Argos a daruruwan shaguna da kuma wasu wuraren Habitat tun lokacin da ya sayi duka biyu shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ƙari da ya ce ya haɓaka tallace-tallace na kayan masarufi kuma ya sa sayayya ta zama mafi riba.
Ƙoƙarin da kamfanin ya yi na sake gina sashen kayan kwalliya da kantin magani ya gaza.
Sainsbury's ya yi ƙoƙari ya yi aiki tare da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma haɗin gwiwa ya ƙare bayan jayayya game da yadda za a raba ribar da ake samu daga kantin magani a cikin manyan kantuna.
Sabuwar dabarar ta zo ne bayan Sainsbury's ta sayar da kasuwancin kantin magani na 281 zuwa Celesio, mai mallakar gidan kantin sayar da kantin Lloyds don £ 125 miliyan shekaru uku da suka gabata.
Ta ce Lloyds za ta taka rawa a shirin, ta hanyar fadada samfuran samfuran fata na kayan kwalliya, gami da La Roche-Posay da Vichy, a cikin shagunan hudu.
Manajan kasuwanci na Sainsbury's, Paul Mills-Hicks ya ce: "Mun kawo sauyi a yadda kayayyakin kwalliyarmu suke kama da yadda suke ji, don inganta yanayin da abokan cinikinmu ke ciki.
Bugu da ƙari, mun saka hannun jari a cikin ma'aikatan da suka ƙware sosai waɗanda za su iya ba da shawara a wurin.
An tsara mu don mu bi kowane irin yanayi, kuma yanayinmu da kuma wurin da muke zama ya sa mu zama wurin da ake son sayen kayayyakin kwalliya da ke saɓa wa al'adarmu ta dā".
Peter Jones ya fusata bayan da Holly Willoughby ta soke yarjejeniyar da ta kai dala miliyan 11.
Tauraron gidan talabijin na Dragons Den, Peter Jones, ya nuna fushinsa bayan da mai watsa shiri Holly Willoughby ya soke yarjejeniyar dala miliyan 11 da ya yi da alamar salon rayuwarsa don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarsa da Marks & Spencer da ITV
Gaskiyar ita ce, Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don kayan ado da kayan aiki.
An yi la'akari da haɗin gwiwar su biyu kamar alamar Goop ta Gwyneth Paltrow.
Mai gabatar da shirin This Morning mai shekara 37 ta sanar da ficewarta a wani sakon Instagram.
Holly Willaby ta bar tauraron wasan kwaikwayon Dragons Den Peter Jones a cikin fushi ta hanyar soke aikinta a ƙarshen lokacin a cikin salon rayuwarsu na biyu - don mai da hankali kan kwangilarta mai yawa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyin sun ce Jones ya amsa da "haushi" lokacin da tauraron talabijin ya sanar a wani taron tashin hankali a ranar Talata a hedkwatar daular kasuwancinsa a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sakamakon sabbin yarjejeniyoyinta - da suka kai fam 1.5 - ba ta da isasshen lokacin da za ta ba da ita ga kayan aikin gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An yi la'akari da haɗin gwiwar su biyu kamar alamar Goop ta Gwyneth Paltrow kuma ana tsammanin za ta ninka kuɗin Willoughby, wanda aka kiyasta ya kai £ 11 miliyan.
A lokacin da Willaby mai shekara 37 ta wallafa a shafin Instagram cewa tana barin Truly, Jones yana kan jirgin sama daga Burtaniya zuwa ɗayan wuraren hutunsa.
A cewar wata majiya: "Truly babu shakka shine babban fifiko ga Holly.
Wannan ya kamata ya zama makomar ta na dogon lokaci wanda zai samar mata da kudin shiga na shekaru masu zuwa.
Wannan shawarar ta sa kowa ya yi mamaki.
Babu wanda ya yarda da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, yana kusa da ƙaddamarwa.
"Kayan ajiyar kamfanin a Marlowe suna cike da kayayyaki da suke shirye don sayarwa".
Masana sun yi imanin cewa barin mai gabatar da wannan safiya, wanda shine daya daga cikin taurari masu samun kudin shiga a Burtaniya, na iya kashe kamfanin miliyoyin saboda saka hannun jari mai yawa a cikin kayayyaki daban-daban, daga alkukin da kyandirori zuwa tufafin gida, da kuma yiwuwar ƙarin jinkiri a ƙaddamarwa.
Kuma hakan zai iya kawo ƙarshen abota mai tsawo.
Willaby, mahaifiyar yara uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance abokai na Jones da matarsa Tera Cappe na shekaru goma.
Willaby ta kafa Truly tare da Cap a 2016, kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga matsayin shugaban kamfanin a watan Maris.
Ma'auratan sun yi hutu tare kuma Jones ya mallaki kashi 40 cikin dari na kamfanin talabijin na Baldwin.
Willaby za ta zama jakadan M&S kuma za ta maye gurbin Annette McFarlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin ITV na I'm A Celebrity.
Wani majiya da ke kusa da Jones ya ce a daren jiya, "Ba mu da wata magana game da harkokin kasuwancinsa".
"Sai muka soma soyayya".
Ya yi ba'a game da sukar da ya samu daga jaridu kan maganganun da wasu ke kira "marasa shugaban kasa" da kuma cewa yana da kyakkyawan fata game da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa.
Me ya sa Shugaba Trump ya yi sassauci sosai?
"In ji Trump a cikin muryar mai gabatar da labarai.
"Ban yi wata sadaukarwa ba".
Ya ce Kim na sha'awar ganawa ta biyu bayan ya yaba da ganawarsu ta farko a watan Yuni a matsayin babban mataki na kawar da makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa.
Amma tattaunawar ta dakatar da makaman nukiliya.
Fiye da watanni uku bayan taron da aka yi a watan Yuni a Singapore, babban jami'in diflomasiyyar Koriya ta Arewa, Ri Yong Ho, ya shaida wa shugabannin duniya a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa Koriya ta Arewa ba ta ganin "amsawa" daga Amurka ga matakan farko na kwance makamai da Koriya ta Arewa ta dauka.
Maimakon haka, a cewarsa, Amurka ta ci gaba da sanya takunkumi da nufin ci gaba da matsa lamba.
