Guguwar Rosa ta yi barazanar ambaliyar ruwa a Phoenix, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City
Ba kasafai ake samun ruwan sama mai zafi a Arizona ba, amma wannan shine abin da ake tsammanin zai faru a farkon mako mai zuwa, lokacin da ragowar guguwar Rosa ta mamaye hamadar kudu maso gabas kuma ta kawo barazanar ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta bayyana barazanar ambaliyar iska a ranakun biyu da uku ga yammacin Arizona zuwa kudu maso gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, gami da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
Ana sa ran guguwar Rosa za ta wuce Phoenix a ranar Talata, kuma za ta yi nisa da yammacin Litinin tare da ruwan sama.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Phoenix ta wallafa a shafinta na Twitter cewa guguwa 10 ne kawai suka samu matsayin guguwa ko guguwa mai zafi a cikin nisan mil 200 daga Phoenix tun shekarar 1950!
Hurricane Katrina (1967) wani hadari ne da ya kai nisan mil 40 daga iyakar Arizona.
Kwanan nan, Cibiyar Hurricane ta Arizona ta yi hasashen ruwan sama na 50 zuwa 100 mm, tare da wasu adadin har zuwa 150 mm a gefen Arizona.
Sauran yankuna a cikin hamadar kudu maso yamma, gami da Rocky Mountains da Babban Basin, ana sa ran samun 25 zuwa 50 mm, tare da yiwuwar wuraren da ke da nisa da samun 50 mm duka.
Ga wadanda ke wajen yankin da ake fuskantar ambaliyar ruwa, ruwan sama daga guguwar Rosa na iya zama albarka saboda yankin ya sha wahala daga fari.
Ko da yake ambaliyar ruwa tana da matukar hadari, wasu daga cikin wadannan ruwan sama za su taimaka saboda yankin kudu maso yammacin kasar na fama da fari.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Fari ta Amirka, sama da kashi 40 cikin ɗari na Arizona suna cikin matsanancin fari, wanda shi ne na biyu mafi tsanani, in ji weather.com.
Da farko, hanyar guguwar Rosa za ta kai gaci a duk fadin yankin Baja California a Mexico.
Guguwar Rosa, wacce har yanzu ta kasance guguwa a safiyar Lahadi tare da iyakar iska mai saurin kilomita 137 a awa daya, tana da nisan kilomita 620 kudu da Punta Eugena, Mexico, tana tafiya arewa da sauri kimanin kilomita 20.
Guguwar ta yi karo da ruwan sanyi a tekun Pacific, don haka ta yi rauni.
Saboda haka ana sa ran ta isa Mexico a matsayin guguwa mai karfi a ranar Litinin da yamma ko yamma.
Ruwan sama a sassan Mexico na iya zama mai tsanani kuma yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa.
Ana sa ran samun ruwan sama mai tsawon millimeter 75 zuwa 150 daga gabashin California zuwa arewa maso yammacin Sonora, tare da yiwuwar zuwa millimeter 250, in ji weather.com.
Bayan haka, guguwar Rosa za ta ci gaba zuwa Mexico a matsayin guguwa mai zafi, kafin ta isa iyakar Arizona a farkon safiyar Talata a matsayin guguwa mai zafi, wanda zai ci gaba a Arizona zuwa kudancin Utah a ranar Talata da dare.
"Babban hadarin da ake tsammani daga guguwar Rosa, ko kuma ta bar ta, shi ne ruwan sama mai yawa a Baja California, kudu maso yammacin Sonora da kuma hamadar kudu maso yammacin Amurka, in ji Cibiyar Guguwar Kasa.
Ana sa ran wannan ruwan sama zai haifar da ambaliyar ruwa da kuma kwararar shara mai hatsari a cikin hamada, da kuma ambaliyar ƙasa a yankunan tsaunuka.
