Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara zanga-zangar neman zaben a yau da daddare a Wheeling, Virginia.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko na tsayawa biyar da Trump ya shirya yi a wannan makon, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka kada kuri'ar amincewa da nadin da aka yi masa na zama alkalin kotun koli, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na cikin hatsarin rasa iko a majalisar dokoki bayan zaben da aka yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana yau da dare kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa ta yanar gizo?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya farawa da karfe 7:00 na yammacin yammacin yamma, ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za a iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a kan YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana ne game da sauraron da aka yi a wannan makon game da dan takarar kotun koli, Bert Kawano, wanda ya zama mai tsanani game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i kuma ya haifar da jinkirta jefa kuri'a a cikin sati guda yayin da FBI ke binciken zargin.
Amma babban manufar wannan gangamin shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
Saboda haka, shugaban kasar Trump ya ce manufar taron biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa shi ne karfafa masu sa kai da kuma tallafawa yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa, wanda shugaban ya shirya ziyartar kasashe da dama a lokacin da ake fuskantar babban zaben", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron na yau da daddare, wanda aka shirya a filin wasa na West Bank a Wheeling, na iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ya kiyasta.
A ranar Asabar ne dai Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya samu rinjaye da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Republican daga West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don kokarin inganta matsayinsa a zaben", in ji Simon Hyder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
