Turai ta yi gaba da ci 10-6 a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder
Turai na da fa'ida sosai a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan da ta kammala wasannin hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ci 10 da 6 a kan Amurka.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa Tommy Fleetwood da Wrencesco Molinari sun jagoranci canjin tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods mai gwagwarmaya, wanda ya kara nisa zuwa yanzu a Le Golf National zuwa maki hudu.
'Yan wasan kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai, Thomas Bjorn, wadanda suka yi kokarin kare kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, sun yi nasara a kan 'yan wasan Amurkawa da suka rasa a wasannin hudu da safe, kuma suka kawo wasan zuwa 3-1.
