Fleetwood shine dan Turai na farko da ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, waɗanda aka lakabi da "Hollywood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, sune kawai biyu da suka ci kwallaye hudu daga cikin wasannin farko na Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kafa hudu, sun ci gaba da aiki tare don doke Woods da aka raunana da kuma sabon dan wasan Amurka Bryson DeCambeau da karin haske 5 da 4.
