Justin Rose, wanda ya huta a wasannin kwallon kafa hudu da safe, ya dawo don shiga Henrik Stenson a wasannin hudu don doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka da ci 2 da 1 - wadanda ke kan gaba a duniya.
