Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da ya dace" da yake so sun hada da tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore, da kuma sauye-sauye a cikin daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Dalibai a Harvard suna daukar darasi kan yadda za su samu isasshen hutu.
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara yana koya wa mahalarta yadda za su yi barci sosai, a ƙoƙarin magance al'adar koyo ta hanyar kasancewa a farke duk dare tare da maganin kafeyin.
Wani bincike da aka yi ya nuna cewa ɗaliban jami'a mafi girma a duniya ba su da masaniya game da yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Kessler, farfesa a fannin ilimin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya ce shi ne na farko a kasar.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don fara wannan darasi bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci akan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshen wannan jawabin, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa aka gaya mini wannan a wannan shekarar, a makarantar sakandare?"
Ta ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci - abin da ya ba ni mamaki, "in ji shi ga jaridar Telegraph.
Wannan karatun, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a wannan shekara, yana bayyana wa ɗalibai ƙa'idodin yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke taimakawa aikin ilimi da wasanni, da haɓaka yanayin su gaba ɗaya.
Paul Breyer, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a makarantar likitancin Harvard da kuma babban darektan kula da kiwon lafiya a jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar bude karatun ne bayan gano cewa dalibai sun sha wahala daga rashin bacci sosai a makon.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani ɓangaren, an nuna hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai suke latsa kofi, labule, tufafin motsa jiki da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin yin bacci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dindindin zai iya kara hadarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, bakin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da alamomi masu ma'amala, suna ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da al'amuran yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa hakan ba zai canja halayen ɗalibanmu ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da 'yancin sanin hakan - kamar yadda kai ma kake da 'yancin sanin sakamakon shan taba", in ji Farfesa Schießler.
Ya ce al'adar alfahari da "barci da daddare" ta ci gaba, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da matsin lamba ga dalibai na kara haifar da matsalar rashin bacci.
Kulawa da isasshen barci, da ingancin bacci, ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na kowane ɗalibi don yaƙi da damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, in ji shi - har ma don guje wa kiba, saboda rashin bacci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, don haka muna fama da yunwa koyaushe.
Raymond Sue, wani ɗalibi mai shekaru 19 daga California wanda ke nazarin ilimin kimiyyar halitta da kimiyyar lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Schießler wajen tsara wannan darasi, bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya haskaka idanunsa kuma ya motsa shi ya ƙarfafa darasi a ko'ina a harabar makarantar.
