Wannan hanya ta hada da cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga mai haƙuri, kuma maye gurbin kwayoyin a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Bayan haka, kwayoyin zasu iya ganin furotin da ya zama ruwan dare gama gari ga yawancin nau'ikan ciwon daji sannan kuma a sake saka su cikin mai haƙuri.
Wani allurar rigakafi na gwaji yana nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a cikin marasa lafiya da nau'ikan cututtukan daji.
A wata mata da ta yi allurar rigakafin, wadda ke koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki yadda za ta gane ƙwayoyin cutar kansa, cutar kansa ta ovarian ta ɓace cikin watanni 18.
Wannan ya kunshi cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin mai haƙuri, canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su iya gano furotin da ake kira HER2 wanda yake da yawa a cikin cututtukan daji, sannan kuma a sake saka su cikin mai haƙuri.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, daga Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa muna da allurar rigakafi mai matukar alkawura".
HER2 tana hana ci gaban wasu nau'ikan ciwon daji, gami da nono, ovaries, huhu da kuma babban hanji, in ji Farfesa Berzowski.
Irin wannan tsarin na daukar kwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya da kuma koya musu yadda za su kai hari kan kwayoyin cutar kansa ya yi tasiri wajen magance cutar sankarar bargo.
