An sake janye sayan sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
An shirya sabon jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma an jinkirta shi na aƙalla shekara guda, saboda lalacewar tsarin da rage farashin, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An dakatar da karbar Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgin ruwan sabon rukunin Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar wani rahoton jaridar Die Zeit da ya ambato wani kakakin soja.
An shirya jirgin zai shiga rundunar a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da ke tattare da shi sun hana shi cimma burin.
Dukkanin jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg, wanda rundunar sojan ruwa ta samu tun a shekarar 2007, za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Ana sa ran sun hada da babban bindiga, batirin makamai masu linzami da na jirgin sama da kuma fasahohin da ba a san su ba, kamar siginar sauti, infrared da rage radar.
Sauran mahimman fasali sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - za a iya tura sabbin jirage na zamani har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashar jirgin ruwa.
Duk da haka, jinkiri na yau da kullun yana nufin cewa sabbin jiragen ruwa - waɗanda za su ba da damar tura sojojin Jamus zuwa ƙasashen waje - za su zama tsofaffi a lokacin da suka fara aiki, in ji de Zeit.
An samu labarin jirgin ruwan mai suna F125 a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ki karbar jirgin ruwan kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta dawo da wani jirgi zuwa wani jirgin ruwa bayan da aka dakatar da shi.
Ba a san dalilai da yawa ba game da dalilin dawowar, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu mahimman kayan aiki da kayan aiki da suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani don amfani da aikin yaƙi.
Rashin software ya kasance da mahimmanci saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class za su yi aiki da kimanin ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - kusan rabin ma'aikatan da aka yi amfani da su a cikin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa, nau'in Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyin kima wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya rage ikon Navy don ƙara haɓakawa a nan gaba.
Nauyin jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz ya kai tan 7,000, kuma ya ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga rashin ingancin software, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horar da ma'aikata - ma ya zama matsala.
An yi jita-jita cewa ya kai euro biliyan 3.1 (dala biliyan 3.6) - sama da euro biliyan 2.2 na asali.
Matsalolin da ke damun sabbin jiragen ruwa na zama masu matukar muhimmanci musamman idan aka yi la'akari da cewa sojojin ruwan Jamus na raguwa.
Tun a farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya tabbatar da cewa a yau, sojojin ruwa na da jiragen ruwa da zasu iya yin aiki.
Majiyar ta ce matsalar ta kara tsanantawa da kuma kara tsanantawa a tsawon lokaci, saboda an kori tsofaffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a maye gurbinsu da wasu ba.
Ya nuna rashin jin daɗi cewa ba za a iya haɗa jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg ba.
