Wani sabon bincike da aka yi a wani gida a tsaunukan Scotland ya nuna yadda jemage suke amfani da shimfidar wuri wajen neman abinci.
Ana fatan cewa binciken zai ba da sabon haske game da halayen tsuntsaye masu tsalle-tsalle na musamman kuma zai taimaka wajen jagorantar ayyukan kiyayewa a nan gaba.
